Security Guarantees

‚ùå Stops supply-chain tampering

A single-bit change in weights or architecture is detected.

‚ùå Stops malicious ONNX / TorchScript trojans

Architecture-hash fails ‚Üí immediate quarantine.

‚ùå Stops silent model swaps

Any unapproved file is rejected.

‚ùå Stops pickle-based RCE

Pickle is forbidden by manifest + Hades.

‚ùå Stops fine-tuning attempts to smuggle payloads

Fine-tuned weights ‚â† Golden Manifest ‚Üí rejected.

‚ùå Stops operator-level backdoors

Multi-sig signatures prevent single-key malicious upgrades.

‚ùå Enables perfect forensic auditing

Hermit Crab ledger records all events in hash-linked blocks.

