Fundamental Invariant

A model may speak only if its computed architecture and parameter hashes exactly match those in its Golden Manifest.

Violations ‚Üí BLOCK.
No exceptions, no overrides, no backdoors.

Pantheon-Prime becomes immune to entire classes of model-level exploits.

